longBusinessSummary: Embry Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, designs, researches, develops, manufactures, trades in, and sells ladies brassieres, panties, swimwear, and sleepwear. The company sells its lingerie products primarily under the EMBRY FORM, FANDECIE, COMFIT, E-BRA, IVU, IADORE, and LIZA CHENG brands. It also holds trademark and invests in properties. The company operates retail outlets comprising concessionary counters, and retail stores in Mainland China, Hong Kong, and Macau. It also operates an online shop. The company was founded in 1975 and is headquartered in Kwai Chung, Hong Kong. Embry Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Harmonious World Limited.
